{"tid":2492102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國疫苗無法發揮保護力！ 英專家：不能真正對抗武肺病毒","createTime":"2021-04-16T23:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T07:52:09.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"30e7e2e66a6ea3ba3daa12ed0f3501b1e7208ecc","tid":2492102,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:39:12.000Z","msg":"中國疫苗無法發揮保護力！ 英專家：不能真正對抗武肺病毒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3501542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3501542&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=646ae270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3501542&h=0afbefb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3501542</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國疾病預防控制中心（CDC）主任高福日前罕見承認中國武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫苗的防護力不高，雖然後來改口否認，但仍引起國際關注。英國專家認為，根據智利的數據來看，中國疫苗不足以阻止病毒傳播。<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》 報導，全世界目前至少有53個國家購買中國製的武漢肺炎疫苗，其中大部分是南美、非洲和東南亞的發展中國家，因為對於沒有特殊儲存設備的國家來說，價格便宜且易於存放的中國疫苗是理想選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">智利大學的一項研究發現，中國的科興疫苗接種第1劑的有效率僅3%，隔2週注射第2劑才會提高到56.5%；而在巴西進行的另一項研究顯示，科興疫苗的有效率只有50%，僅略高於世界衛生組織（WHO）可接受的疫苗標準。相較之下，輝瑞（Pfizer）和莫德納（Moderna）疫苗的有效率高達95%及94%，阿斯特捷利康（Astra Zeneca）疫苗的有效率也有達到79%。<br />\n<br />\n英國雷丁大學病毒學家瓊斯（Ian Jones）表示，中國疫苗的生產速度很快，但疫苗所包含的病毒蛋白無法發揮保護作用，注射入人體後很大部分都浪費掉，且這類疫苗並非針對性，導致免疫系統釋放出大量抗體，實際上卻沒有幫助對抗真正的武肺病毒。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國生產的科興及國藥疫苗均屬於滅活疫苗，利用武肺病毒的滅活版本進行基因改造，經處理後再將病毒細胞注入人體，優點是生產快速。"},{"pid":"f6844b276bf20e0d4b4002b225fe1643b4d724b2","tid":2492102,"uid":266519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:58:11.000Z","msg":"中國疫苗不對付中國病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1672ba9117746f84247c4ee5c9a9860fec7d7b81","tid":2492102,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea716497ad3a8df535ab66db5130a615d93cb952","tid":2492102,"uid":207767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"你估真係為左俾人預防咩，係殺人支那針！<br />\n仲要咁多後遺症<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vM1MpWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvM1MpWr.jpg&h=21edacb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f82d467604e24bab3efb70c5ca517525ae570650","tid":2492102,"uid":45003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:06:39.000Z","msg":"中國疫苗唔係對抗武肺病毒 係減低注射人對病毒心理恐懼"},{"pid":"91d689cab3c2b58083fde2facaf823a8ac686f8b","tid":2492102,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea716497ad3a8df535ab66db5130a615d93cb952","tid":2492102,"uid":207767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"你估真係為左俾人預防咩，係殺人支那針！<br />\n仲要咁多後遺症<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vM1MpWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvM1MpWr.jpg&h=21edacb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:09:28.000Z","msg":"愛支針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fefe6e317fc57a686a4631ef0d7f0f812f50a3","tid":2492102,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6844b276bf20e0d4b4002b225fe1643b4d724b2","tid":2492102,"uid":266519,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:58:11.000Z","msg":"中國疫苗不對付中國病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想<br />\n<br />\n中国人不打中国病毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0795815be7dcc234ef0c69e506d9fb48435a0874","tid":2492102,"uid":82628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T00:18:48.000Z","msg":"永續武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><